fm: int removeDuplicates(vector<int> &nums) {         auto size = nums.size();         if (!size)             return 0;         int i = 0, j = 1;         while (j < size) {             if (nums[j] != nums[i])                 nums[++i] = nums[j];             ++j;         }         return i + 1;     }

fm: vector<int> singleNumber(vector<int> &nums) {         int x = 0, s = 1;         for (auto m:nums)             x ^= m;         while ((x & s) == 0)             s <<= 1;         vector<int> ret(2, 0);         for (auto m:nums)             (m & s) == 0 ? ret[0] ^= m : ret[1] ^= m;         return ret;     }
